data.text:
Bruce Cabot Palmer of Tyngsborough, MA died Thursday July 13, 2023 at Westford House.

He was married to the late Harve Bijeol of Tyngsborough Ma.

Born in Watertown, MA on December 17, 1948 he was the son of the late Merrill and Myrtle Palmer.

He is survived by his step daughters Brenda Feeney of Tyngsboro, MA. & Robin Pincence of Plaistow, NH.

At his request all services are private. Arrangements by Dolan Funeral Home 106 Middlesex St. Chelmsford MA 01863
